          "date": "2013-04-24 19:39:31.000000000",
          "tz": -240
        },
        "subject": "LU-2932: increase hash buckets for improved perf",
        "message": "LU-2932: increase hash buckets for improved perf\n\nWith many clients, it is easy have many locks outstanding. This can\noverload the hash table and cause poor performance when looking for a\nlock. This patch suggested by Oleg Drokin should improve performance in\nthese cases.\n\nSigned-off-by: Kit Westneat <kwestneat@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I4f21e3f11706748ff4cf7af8a4efcb891aed4ffa\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/b1_8"
    }
